              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Weighted FLOP cost of an einsum operation."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Uses the whole-expression direct-event accumulation model:\ntotal = (k-1) * prod(M) + prod(alpha), where M is the number of\nunique output elements and alpha is the number of unique output+\nreduction-axis combinations. FMA = 2 (textbook): the \u03b1/M formula counts\nmultiplies and adds separately by construction."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
